Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.73,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Am I gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.11,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You did die...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.45,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.00,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Inga...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:41.89,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be like this, head in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:48.23,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to escape from this saturated world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:53.99,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes like whispering sand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.70,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,These circumstances, unchanging
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.74,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,gazing out at a dreamless tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:07.79,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna say goodbye to the confusion of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:13.26,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I try reaching out, as if to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:18.97,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,We cry millions of times and then get born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:22.18,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with these red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:25.39,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,to that pictured future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:30.94,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Come here right by me, I'm clapping my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.03,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:37.45,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Strain my eyes in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:43.04,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see anything, don't know anything, but I'll still go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:49.42,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,To the place of shining light in which you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:49.00,Episode Num,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.00,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"{\b1}Murder{\b0} at the Ball"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.00,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi’s\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Ango Detective Stories)\N"The Murder at the Ball"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.30,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't feel like doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.39,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.51,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(250,0)}{\b1}Kaishou{\b0} Rie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.51,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(250,0)}Daughter of Kaishou Rinroku\NLives at Home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.18,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,It's a party thrown by the Kanou Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.39,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,A 19th century ball gown is a pain, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.56,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,The skirt's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.81,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,And the corset like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.48,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,You've read up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.65,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fade(300,0)}Kaishou Family Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.65,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fade(300,0)}Head maid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:06.81,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:07.69,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,In manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:08.65,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:09.98,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.11,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,President Kanou himself sent over this dress for his costume party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.28,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a normal design, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.41,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Give a girl some warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.66,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,This way, you won't cause any embarrassment as the master's proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.96,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Proxy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:30.05,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,On TV, they say that President Kanou is gonna be arrested today or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.80,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,They say nothing but groundless things on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:40.51,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there's {\i1}no{\i0} way I'm going to that party alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.40,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,That looks great on you, Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.61,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.65,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been a real bear putting that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.24,Name,Sign,0090,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\b1}Kaishou{\b0} Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.24,Name Sub,Sign,0090,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}Chairman of Japan Justice Network System Holdings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:59.37,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, Japan constructed the Rokumeikan to hold balls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.91,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,with the aim of entering into fair treaties with foreign countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.37,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-san's idea is to go back to basics
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.17,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,and look at international relations with fresh eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.29,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to make it, but give him my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.38,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.71,Main Dialog,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Ms. Koyama from the Public Prosecutor's Office just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.38,Name,Sign,0120,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\b1}Koyama{\b0} Izumi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.38,Name Sub,Sign,0120,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}Public Prosecutor's Office, Joint Coordinating Dept.\NPublic Prosecutor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:14.63,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.89,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou. I heard you weren't going to Kanou's party this evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:19.60,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.60,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a friend of Kanou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:25.18,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, you're an outside adviser to us prosecutors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:25.77,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.10,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is an opportunity for you to question Kanou directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:36.07,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,This evening, I'm acting as Kaishou Rinroku's proxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.32,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Such a contrarian...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:47.21,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is reserved! Please take another elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.25,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky day! It's almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.12,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:49.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead. Top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.54,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.75,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.25,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you two have at this evening's party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.30,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.88,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,300)\shad0\bord0}{\b1}Yuuki{\b0} Shinjurou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.88,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,0)\bord0\shad0}Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you weren't the ones who sent these to us, Prosecutor Koyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.76,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! Why would I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.14,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Ms. Koyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.76,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.06,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.93,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you go near them, your dress will get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.73,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.27,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,300)\shad0\bord0}{\b1}In{\b0}ga
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.27,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\bord1\fade(300,300)\shad0\bord0}Detective's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.48,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.90,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.65,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chairman Kaishou's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.44,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Rinroku's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.49,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you address the Chairman by name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.53,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What? These days, a shady net business success has a monopoly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:26.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,on money and technology, and is an adviser to every ministry and agency. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.62,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're Napoleon too, Kanda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.75,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,My wife told me this was the only way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.76,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,You international banks always prosper after a fire, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.76,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}Ono{\b0} Ittou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.76,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Member of the Liberal Citizens Party
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.47,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.76,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\b1}Kanda{\b0} Masahiko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.76,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fade(300,0)}Representative of the Japanese Branch of the International Currency Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.47,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you, Member.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:43.01,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I wonder how Kanou-san is dealing with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:47.43,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,The prosecutor, and especially the newly-established Joint Coordinating Dept.,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.39,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,intend to arrest him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.48,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, then we'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.23,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,200)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\b1}Kanou{\b0} Nobuzane
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.23,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,200)\c&HFFFFFF&}President of Kanou Group General Trading Company
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.19,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}{\b1}Kanou{\b0} Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.19,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}Nobuzane's Wife and Group's Corporate President
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.95,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-san! Thank you for the invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:02.95,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.83,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Arresting you would be runaway abuse of the prosecutor's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.58,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use tonight's party to again clear you of all suspicion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.67,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I'm going to cause you two undue trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.63,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard on you too, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.80,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Why, having to hold a party in your own building...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.67,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid to even leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.14,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.89,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs26}"No matter how many times we're stepped on,\NJapan will always rise"\N Party Sponsor: Kanou Group General Trading Company
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.14,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I've come as Kaishou Rinroku's proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.56,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.81,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.10,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.61,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Kaishou's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.56,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.28,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had the opportunity to meet Mr. Kaishou,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.86,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,but let me take this occasion to greet his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.28,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Then Professor Kaishou actually exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.78,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Chairman here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:46.83,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.79,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.54,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:48.91,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.41,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:49.70,Main Dialog,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.41,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.38,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.50,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.88,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you're at the party, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.47,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou supports President Kanou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.89,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It shows that he believes in his innocence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:12.02,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello, President Kanou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for inviting me here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.02,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.27,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,In fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.15,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,He is a beacon of light in this chaotic world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.45,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,People call him the Last Great Detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.74,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.41,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki? I've heard that name before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.66,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that always shows up at crime scenes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.71,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,to criticize Chairman Kaishou's brilliant deductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.92,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The newspapers have dubbed him, "The Defeated Detective".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.25,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:45.80,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,However, calling me in means that some crime is going to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.93,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And a major crime at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.06,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,First Kanou, then they try to ingratiate themselves with Chairman Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.64,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They have no principles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.18,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.81,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yuuki Shinjurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.98,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,The Defeated Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.44,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,No one is a greater patriot than Kanou Nobuzane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.40,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,These suspicions against him stem from nothing more than
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.36,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,the state yielding to pressure from foreign countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.20,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-kun, I give you my word that we will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:15.29,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:19.08,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Continuing on, I would be honored to hear a few words from Kanda Masahiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.00,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the Japanese representative for the International Currency Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.00,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Ono passes on reconstruction work to Kanou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.38,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and Kanda puts up financial backing received from other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:30.43,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But somewhere in this triangle, the money goes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.93,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.89,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right now, President Kanou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.14,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What do you people want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.65,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were with the detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:42.40,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that business before was an attempt to help me, was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.40,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the Defeated Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.03,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a room above this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.74,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,This whole floor is President Kanou's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.33,Main Dialog,SP,0000,0000,0000,,How did {\i1}you{\i0} know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.66,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.91,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fade(300,0)}{\b1}Terada{\b0} Ryouko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.91,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}Metro Police Department SP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:55.91,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:01.34,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you didn't have to go to the trouble of having the SP guard me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.21,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,SP?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:07.38,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to let anything happen to you, Miss Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.13,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.89,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.10,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,A toast to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.02,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, a toast in the hopes that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.81,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,the suspicions of you prosecutors are soon dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.86,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:25.99,Main Dialog,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.44,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.37,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the alcohol went right to your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.09,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaishou, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.46,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:09:00.60,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, there is something that I, Kanou Nobuzane,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.36,Main Dialog,Kanou,0000,0000,0000,,would like to say regarding the suspicions that are directed at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:07.03,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Does he mean to insist upon his innocence before a large crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.36,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's being a poor loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:25.92,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Madam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.71,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like something's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.35,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hayami, with Metro Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.64,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,The crime squad will be here soon, so preserve the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.02,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fade(300,0)\a5}{\b1}Hayami{\b0} Seigen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.02,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fade(300,0)\a5}Director of the Security Bureau, Metropolitan Police Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.73,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We in the Joint Coordinating Dept. are allowed to use our own judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.56,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,on whether to launch an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.77,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal is in this hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.86,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The person who murdered Kanou Nobuzane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:51.99,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The issue may be not who did it, but rather why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.28,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.29,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Representative Kanda! Member Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.00,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.83,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you two when the lights went out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.67,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.21,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,Imitating your father, Chairman Kaishou, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.26,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,After all, guided by him, a number of difficult cases have been solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.97,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Before the lights went out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.39,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,someone wearing a Napoleon outfit was near the podium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:20.47,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Several people have said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.89,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of us are you accusing of the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.35,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.85,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.61,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanou is suspected of embezzling funds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:31.19,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,for reconstruction support from other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.49,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Member Ono and Mr. Kanda, you're both connected to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.16,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Kanou had been arrested, you both would've been in hot water...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.87,Main Dialog,Ono,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! When the lights went out, I was talking to Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.62,Main Dialog,Kanda,0000,0000,0000,,And I can establish Member Ono's innocence, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.09,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,You both purposely chose to dress as Napoleon, a costume that would stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.67,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,You figured it would support each other's alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.64,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.22,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.98,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Defeated Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.23,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing for you to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:10.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Your father also acts like a detective, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.86,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My father is different from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.74,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,He just gives advice for the sake of this country's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.24,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.87,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Would you move out of the way a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.88,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, this is Chairman Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.63,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaishou Rinroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.72,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I was friends with Kanou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:38.18,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not there now, but I will give you my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.22,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Innumerable difficult cases have been solved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.93,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,due to the wisdom of Chairman Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.68,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's a special adviser to the Joint Coordinating Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.73,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,of the Public Prosecutor's Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:47.94,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father, the criminals are Member Ono and Representative Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.19,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.31,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:55.15,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, they're wearing the same outfit, but they stand out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:12:00.03,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,However, other than that, no one saw anyone suspicious near the podium
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.95,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,just before the lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.12,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but they were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.41,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, they were there, but at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.33,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,they slipped from everyone's consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.88,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:17.05,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I see... SP...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.30,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,The security guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.43,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,These days, when VIPs get together somewhere, it's taken for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.22,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,that security guards or the SP are in position,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.10,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,to the point where they fall under people's radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.48,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that the SP murdered Kanou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:32.52,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.11,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.99,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou... My husband didn't stuff his own pockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.20,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is he took part of the reconstruction funds and supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.24,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,and stashed them somewhere at the request of someone from the government!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.70,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He intended to reveal that here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.83,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But before he could, a government dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.00,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.93,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The residents' elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:06.39,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,She pretended to leave the hall with us, but then went right back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.64,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,and when the room went dark, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.27,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would have been informed of the timing schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.48,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?! Why would you people do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.15,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.40,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}How am I mistaken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.40,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.03,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it in any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.41,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Inga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.45,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The police did it! The prosecutors did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.04,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, even higher than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.29,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You ganged up on Kanou with the Ministry of Self-Defense and killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.13,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.38,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong. You're certainly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.76,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why is her jacket the only thing that's off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:50.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If the police or prosecutors used this woman to assassinate Kanou Nobuzane...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.35,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.10,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,...why is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.61,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,This is a luxurious place for just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.36,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,If the police assassinated him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.20,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,it would be pointless if we found out soon after that an SP did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.54,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you say suicide is out of the question, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:12.12,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But if she meant to exact vengeance on Kanou on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.42,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible she killed herself afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.50,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, she just would've killed him out in the open with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.21,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why a knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.46,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.64,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone wore a black suit here, they could be taken for the SP...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.14,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Someone impersonated the SP?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that person must have chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,the moment the lights went out from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The person caught the SP off guard, shot her to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.36,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,impersonated her, and returned to the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.70,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then, moving naturally, she approached Mr. Kanou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.58,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, there were only two people outside of the hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.42,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.21,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Kanou...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.09,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even joke about such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.88,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,My husband was just murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.84,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Suspecting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.26,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What reason could I have to kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.72,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want to know the reason for that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.81,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That one's out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:14.18,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,This person is... my boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.94,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Inga, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.36,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.15,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,...just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.20,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.12,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.50,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.96,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.01,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.05,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What was your husband to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.34,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,A criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.72,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The man you loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.72,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Or... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:56.23,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... have to answer that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.65,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.82,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.20,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What was your husband to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.21,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.29,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.52,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.31,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He had to be a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.11,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:49.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,She can ask one question, and people have no choice but to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.87,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean he was a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.28,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:58.91,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently, we were at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,In retaliation for seriously dispatching troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.93,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,terrorists launched multiple attacks against us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.26,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I know. There was a war...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.81,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:18.60,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,No Trespassing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.60,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.27,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,During the war, Kanou dedicated his resources
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:25.52,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,to combat terrorism in this country and he was lauded for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:29.15,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, after the war, all they can say is he's lining his pockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.86,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the victims of terrorism are treated as heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:37.04,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we, who survived, were just desperately trying to stay alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.75,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That man lived for this country and I wasn't going to let him be arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.50,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.55,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He became a hero and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.26,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you stabbed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:02.02,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You killed the SP, impersonated her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.31,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But what about proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The SP's jacket was taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:12.45,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, she borrowed the jacket from the SP and then returned to the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:15.37,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, she didn't put the jacket back on the SP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.12,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But at her feet was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.50,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That dress is the kind that can be put on easily, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.12,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then under all that frilly stuff, it's possible to wear pants, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.05,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.30,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Those shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.69,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If the police had killed him, Mr. Kanou wouldn't be a criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.52,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,but the victim of a government conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.82,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you went so far as to murder an innocent SP?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.36,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,More people died in the war, didn't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:59.49,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,During the war, he gathered up supplies from around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.04,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:04.25,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but now it's evil that he survived and made money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.00,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the damned war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.55,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's war's fault that we fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.38,Main Dialog,Atsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.84,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,People get corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.01,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Even saints and heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.60,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:31.03,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Again, it seems I fell just a little short of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:34.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You knew from the beginning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.41,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, as always,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:40.37,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,the woman SP is going to be announced as the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:44.37,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Mrs. Kanou realized before the police
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.00,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,who the killer was and shot her to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.88,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Does that sound okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:54.51,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-san's misappropriation of goods was a false charge, somebody's plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.88,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,This way, his honor stays intact, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful outcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.93,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.32,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did that woman go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:18.70,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.37,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was tired, so she went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.08,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.04,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.87,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:32.75,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My father's deductions were always off and you're actually right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.17,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But my father and Ms. Koyama don't let that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:41.35,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I always lose. That's why I'm the Defeated Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:46.60,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure Mr. Kanou really was a hero to his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.27,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,A hero that desperately protected his family
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.86,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,and his company in this chaotic society...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:55.03,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's a lie, one so beautiful should...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:56.69,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:02.83,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Something beautiful should be allowed to end... while it's still beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.83,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.04,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something that applies to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.33,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Since we'll always be in the process of falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:37.15,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,In the pale morning mist, a whispered prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:45.16,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna follow this twisted landscape with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:53.17,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for the "truth", "a 'lie' will do" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:22:01.55,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tracing it as if we can see through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:05.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:09.48,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a falling feather
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:12.48,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:17.90,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:37.34,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, unravel it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:41.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tattered cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:44.30,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.52,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:53.94,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that the next original story is called "Les Miserables",
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:58.11,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,from Ango Sakaguchi’s Ango Torimonochou (Ango Detective Stories)!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:00.03,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna read it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.03,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what's a sketchy rickshaw man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.32,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Pourboire?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:05.95,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,English Twist?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:13.33,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinjurou! This is a completely different story!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:15.56,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The bad guy is xxxxx, it says!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:18.01,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,There was no xxxxx in our story, right?
